node.text:
Check it out! Our exclusive interview with Kathy Kolla and Shari Belafonte is now live on coolmagazineonline.com! We are so privileged to have had the awesome chance to interview these two super cool ladies about their latest film project "Plastic Daydream"! Stop by our Cool Magazine website (link in bio) or paste this link into your browser:
www.coolmagazineonline.com/kolla-belafonte  to read all about what they had to say about filming, the entertainment biz, #MeToo, vegan eats, The Morning Show and dogs! 
ENJOY!
